block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper plane 17 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. Jumping Jack designed by Andrew Dewar. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 016 : Hunter by Kunihiko Kasahara", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/e9fm86pwLGo Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
